s cyclists and athletes in realtime for events such as professional motorsports horse racing cycling stage races and marathons the imagerecognition tracking software does not require the traditional stationary camera and has been deployed for events including the indianapolis  the kentucky derby the tour de france and the new york city marathon goto boardedit smt’s goto board giant onair talent operated board is a large touchscreen monitor and analysis tool that announcers use to stop and pause video and draganddrop statistics it has been used both in sports and entertainment shows such as mlb network and the bet channel’s   park music video show smart and augmented realityedit smt’s smart system utilizes smt’s imagestitch technology to display graphics and signage within a live virtual scene smart line produces digital markers on a pitch such as the first down marker on a football field and smart vip displays onair graphics including signage billboards and video displays smart studio produces realtime d virtual studios for nbc sunday night football smt has provided augmented reality products such as night vision which can be used on replays to highlight the onfield action by blacking out the field around the players while retaining the yard markers clientsedit smt has provided data and social media for many regional and national tv channels including abc sports nbc sports cbs sports espn new england sports network turner sports tnt yes network noteworthy eventsedit sporting events that have used smt’s products include the super bowl the indianapolis  the kentucky derby summer and winter x games nba games nascar races nhl games awardsedit two  silver telly awards for video production and supporting virtual graphics  promaxbda sports marketing award  davey award tv sports referencesedit  httpwwwsportsvideoorgsvgexclusivesmtacquiressportvisioninmeetingofsportstechnologygiants  httpwwwvicentecapitalcomportfoliophp  httpswwwyoutubecomwatchvtkboeyem  httpsportsvideoorgma